OL,3,CTwo men admit setting fire to bus
OL,4,Cduring Harehills riots
OL,6,FTwo men have admitted setting fire to
OL,7,Fa bus during riots in Leeds sparked by
OL,8,Fchildren from a local family being
OL,9,Ftaken into care.
OL,11,FTrouble broke out after social
OL,12,Fservices were called to deal with a
OL,13,Fchild protection issue on Luxor Street
OL,14,Fin Harehills on July 18.
OL,16,FDuring the unrest a patrol car was
OL,17,Foverturned and a bus set alight,
OL,18,Fforcing passengers to flee.
OL,20,FTensions spilled over after police
OL,21,Farrived to provide back-up.
