OL,3,CTwo men admit setting fire to bus
OL,4,Cduring Harehills riots
OL,6,FOver the course of several hours,
OL,7,Flarge crowds gathered, police were
OL,8,Fattacked with missiles and several
OL,9,Ffires were started.
OL,11,FOn Thursday Mark Mitchell, 34, and
OL,12,FMilan Zamostny, 30, both pleaded
OL,13,Fguilty to arson with recklessness as
OL,14,Fto whether life was endangered.
OL,16,FZamostny, of Luxor Avenue, also
OL,17,Fadmitted a charge of violent disorder
OL,18,Fat Leeds Crown Court.
