OL,6,FMitchell, of Strathmore View, pleaded
OL,7,Fguilty to the same charge at an
OL,8,Fearlier hearing.
OL,10,FBoth men were remanded in custody
OL,11,Funtil their sentencing on October 1.
OL,13,FJudge Guy Kearl KC, the Recorder of
OL,14,FLeeds, told them it was "almost
OL,15,Finevitable that an immediate custodial
OL,16,Fsentence will be passed".
