OL,6,FThe court heard that Zamostny, who
OL,7,Ffollowed proceedings with the help of
OL,8,Fa Romanian interpreter, has learning
OL,9,Fdifficulties and there were
OL,10,F"suggestions" he had been trafficked
OL,11,Finto the UK as a teenager.
OL,13,FEarlier this month Iustin Dobre, 37,
OL,14,Falso pleaded guilty to one count of
OL,15,Farson with recklessness as to whether
OL,16,Flife was endangered over the bus fire.
OL,18,FHe did not enter a plea for a second
OL,19,Fcharge of violent disorder and will
OL,20,Fappear in court for a further hearing
OL,21,Flater on Thursday.
